full_content:
Function: acl_set_qualifier
URL: https://www.qnx.com/developers/docs/7.1/com.qnx.doc.neutrino.lib_ref/topic/a/acl_set_qualifier.html
Synopsis: int acl_set_qualifier( acl_entry_t entry_d,
Headers: #include <sys/acl.h>
Parameters:
  - entry_d: The descriptor of the entry whose qualifier you want to set.
  - tag_qualifier_p: A pointer to the qualifier (see below).
Examples:
Example 1:
#include <sys/acl.h>

int acl_set_qualifier( acl_entry_t entry_d,
                       const void *tag_qualifier_p );
